WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.667 --> 00:00:02.135
AND FINALLY,
WE CAN ALL AGREE

00:00:02.169 --> 00:00:04.972
THAT DONALD STERLING
IS A DISGUSTING BIGOT,

00:00:05.005 --> 00:00:07.574
AND HE GOT WHAT HE DESERVED.

00:00:07.608 --> 00:00:08.575
GO AHEAD.

00:00:08.609 --> 00:00:10.077
LET YOUR VOICES BE HEARD!

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:12.079
LET YOUR VOICES BE HEARD.

00:00:12.112 --> 00:00:14.081
BUT...

00:00:14.114 --> 00:00:16.350
LET'S NOT TURN
A COMPLETE BLIND EYE

00:00:16.383 --> 00:00:18.519
TO THE FACT THAT
THERE'S ANOTHER HORRIBLE PERSON

00:00:18.552 --> 00:00:19.853
IN THIS SITUATION:

00:00:19.887 --> 00:00:23.190
HIS 30-SOMETHING-YEAR-OLD
GOLD-DIGGING MISTRESS.

00:00:23.223 --> 00:00:25.526
SHE'S GETTING OFF PRETTY EASY
IF YOU ASK ME.

00:00:25.559 --> 00:00:28.695
YOU KNOW WHO DOESN'T BANG
A MARRIED 80-YEAR-OLD RACIST

00:00:28.729 --> 00:00:30.197
FOR FOUR YEARS?

00:00:30.230 --> 00:00:32.533
A GOOD PERSON.

00:00:32.566 --> 00:00:36.937
IT'S GETTING TO WHERE
YOU CAN'T TRUST A LADY ANYMORE.

00:00:36.970 --> 00:00:38.639
WHY IS EVERYONE
ALWAYS SECRETLY RECORDING

00:00:38.672 --> 00:00:39.640
THE PEOPLE THEY LOVE?

00:00:39.673 --> 00:00:41.108
MY GIRLFRIEND CAN FEEL FREE

00:00:41.141 --> 00:00:43.110
TO LEAK OUR PRIVATE
CONVERSATIONS ANYTIME.

00:00:43.143 --> 00:00:44.411
I'M AN OPEN BOOK.

00:00:59.826 --> 00:01:02.129
THANK GOODNESS
SHE DIDN'T FILM THAT

00:01:02.162 --> 00:01:02.229
BECAUSE I WAS SAYING ALL THAT
IN BLACKFACE.

